summary: This document details the arrest of Alfredo Rodriguez on December 15, 2009, pursuant to a warrant for obstruction of justice. The arrest was executed by FBI agents at a specified location in West Palm Beach, Florida, and Rodriguez was subsequently transported to the Palm Beach County Jail.
